title: Sleek Luxury Studio 1 Bath in Financial District!
posting_body: ['Sabrina Rosal', 'Phone: 201-350-7865', 'Email: <URL>', "This sleek studio 1 Bath features an in-unit washer/dryer, 10' ceilings, white oak finished flooring, and modern kitchens accented with custom paneled appliances and white lacquer cabinetry.", "This luxury high rise offers a 24-hr doorman, outdoor rooftop pool, residents' lounge, fitness center, and yoga studio.", 'Located in the heart of the Financial District which features an all-access transportation hub including major subway lines (A/C/J/Z/2/3/4/5/R/W), PATH, and NYC ferries.', 'This neighborhood features local restaurants, attractions, and beautiful waterfront views to enjoy the city!', 'LISTING #138448', 'Building Amenities', 'Doorman', 'Elevator', 'Health Club', 'Pool', 'Subway', 'New Construction', 'Laundry', 'Bicycle Room', 'Storage', 'Lounge', 'Valet', 'Roof Deck', 'Wheelchair Access', 'WiFi', 'Common Outdoor Space', 'Receiving Room', 'Business Center', 'Apartment Amenities', 'Dishwasher', 'Hardwood', 'High Ceilings', 'Laundry In Unit', 'Sabrina Rosal', 'Phone: 201-350-7865', 'Email: <URL>', 'To view, call or text Sabrina Rosal at:', '201-350-7865', 'Email: <URL>']
